text: The Homestretch is a 1947 American drama movie directed by H. Bruce Humberstone and starring Cornel Wilde, Maureen O'Hara, Glenn Langan, Helen Walker, James Gleason, Henry Stephenson, Margaret Bannerman. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. == Other websites == * * Category:1947 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by H. Bruce Humberstone
